<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>User Access Review</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                background-color: #f2f2f2;
            }
            .container {
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
                background-color: #fff;
                border-radius: 5px;
                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            }
            h1 {
                color: #333;
                text-align: center;
            }
            p {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }
            .signature {
                font-style: italic;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>User Access Review</h1>
            <p>Dear Manager,</p>
            <p>We are conducting a user access review and we need your help. As a manager, you are responsible for ensuring that your team members have the appropriate access to the systems and applications they need to do their jobs.</p>
            <p>Please complete the audit by reviewing the access levels of your team members and confirming that they have the appropriate access. If you identify any discrepancies or issues, please let us know as soon as possible.</p>
            <p>You can access the application for performing the audit using this <a href="#">link.</a></p>
            <p>Please use your DN name "<%= managerDn %>" and your company credentials to login to the system.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>
            <p class="signature">Sincerely,<br>The User Access Review Team</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
